               <p>GEORGE PRITCHARD. On the 31st of July I was bathing near <placeName id="t18260914-362-crimeloc2037">Maiden-lane-bridge</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-362-crimeloc2037" type="placeName" value="Maiden-lane-bridge"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-362-crimeloc2037" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-362-off2035 t18260914-362-crimeloc2037"></join>, and lost my coat from the bank - I saw the prisoner put it on and walk away - I got out, and called Stop thief! he pulled it off and ran away - I saw him in custody.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by Mr. PHILLIPS. Q. What time was this? A. About eight o'clock; he had no other coat on.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-362-person1916">
